<HEADLINE> Ugandan Army Intensifies Attacks on Rebels </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, September 7 (Xinhua) -- The Ugandan army has
intensified attacks on the rebel Lord's Resistance Army (LRA) in
the north, killing six and injuring dozens in the latest attack,
the New Vision daily reported Thursday.
</P>
