Museveni will visit Hoima district in the western region Friday to
assess the deteriorating security situation there, the New Vision
daily reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Museveni has canceled his trip to the United Nations Millennium
Summit in New York, United States, the report said.
</P>
<P>
