Allied Democratic Forces rebels in the area. The raiders have
mostly hit Kyangwali and Kabwoya, killing dozens of people and
leaving several displaced in the last five months.
</P>
<P>
The residents have expressed welcome to Museveni's visit,
saying it will give soldiers morale to flash out the rebels, the
report said. 
