away in her taxi, after he forced the woman to get out of her car
in the suburbs of the city.
</P>
<P>
The police chased after Du who drove erratically and knocked
down 15 students and two more students subsequently.
</P>
<P>
Du was not apprehended until police shot out one of the taxi's
tyres.
</P>
<P>
Du was from Wudaohe Village, Badai Township of north China's
Inner Mongolian Autonomous Region.
</P>
<P>
The case is being investigated further. 
