<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, September 7 (Xinhua) -- Four persons were killed and
17 others injured when a Colombo bound intercity bus collided with
a bus carrying navy officers in the central hilly part of Sri
Lanka, police said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
